Package one.block.eosiojavaabieosserializationprovider

Provides the classes necessary to wrap the ABIEOS c++ serialization provider implementation.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbiEosJson
    This class holds the JSON templates for ABI conversion as immutable static Maps.
    AbiEosSerializationProviderImpl
    Implementation of ISerializationProvider based on a native C++ transformation process compiled via the NDK for Android.
    JsonUtils
    Provides static utility classes for converting JSON to different formats.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AbieosContextNullError
    Error class is used when there is an exception when the ABIEOS c++ code attempts to create its working context during initialization.

Package one.block.eosiojavaabieosserializationprovider Description

Provides the classes necessary to wrap the ABIEOS c++ serialization provider implementation. The main class is AbiEosSerializationProviderImpl
